---
title: Fig-Maple Double Pork Tenderloin with Brussels Sprouts and Garlic Roasted Potatoes
description: Pork loves making friends with a sweet sauce. Tonight, pan-seared and oven-finished pork tenderloin pairs up with a lip-smackin' good fig-maple sauce to put a smile on your face! Garlicky roasted potatoes and buttery Brussels sprouts make this a beautifully-composed plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/filet-de-porc-double-aux-figues-et-a-lerable-b65b0931.jpg
